{"tid":1113571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"錦上路7私家車遭刮花刑毀","createTime":"2019-04-18T03:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T06:04:52.000Z","uid":38757,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da6c5ee9c8a886d557e6a38d7a2545c60e88e784","tid":1113571,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:56:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190418/bkn-20190418100225549-0418_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190418%2Fbkn-20190418100225549-0418_00822_001.html&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSG9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=f5b2af71\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190418/bkn-20190418100225549-0418_00822_001.html</a><br />\n今晨(18日)8時29分，元朗錦上路富銀花園對開，有車主在取車時發現座駕被人用硬物刮花，遂報警調查。警員到場另揭發6輛停泊上址的私家車遭刑毀，正聯絡車主進一步了解，調查歹徒動機。案件列作刑事毀壞，交由刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190418/photo/bkn-20190418100225549-0418_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190418103454\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190418%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190418100225549-0418_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190418103454&h=73777b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190418/photo/bkn-20190418100225549-0418_00822_001_03b.jpg?20190418103454\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190418%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190418100225549-0418_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20190418103454&h=f2521e27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190418/photo/bkn-20190418100225549-0418_00822_001_04b.jpg?20190418103454\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190418%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190418100225549-0418_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20190418103454&h=c34a2950&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"968a4edddc331ff2e9f701ee9802cd17e50f5659","tid":1113571,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,